facing a situation where in most law schools, they

08:26.399 --> 08:39.682
don't teach much about municipal law. They don't 
teach much about planning or land use law. There's

08:41.845 --> 08:42.647
no money in it. You know, why bother? Nobody in his 
right mind is going to do that other than worrying

08:43.669 --> 08:48.036
about the bonds and the financial aspects. Well, 
this guy, because he stayed there for a long period

08:49.096 --> 08:53.580
of time, kept getting promoted. The guy above him 
quits and gets a good job, and he moves up. Well, it

08:59.165 --> 09:15.039
got interesting because it got to the point that I 
was going downstairs, borrowing his law library,

08:59.165 --> 09:15.039
looking things up, and then carrying the open 
volumes into him to talk to him about what we were

08:59.165 --> 09:15.039
getting ready to do and why we could do it.

09:17.321 --> 09:19.002
It also got to the point that He would get put on the 
spot and make some very bad mistakes. There's an

09:23.983 --> 09:27.707
incorporated village on Gallaston Island called 
