would like more time to negotiate, and the clock on 
us incorporating within your extraterritorial

09:48.251 --> 10:00.992
jurisdiction certainly does not stop unless we 
efficiently remove the application. So the

10:01.092 --> 10:07.984
result is Jamaica Beach is the only incorporated 
city on Galveston Island except Galveston. The

